[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +## 17. Localization System Requirements
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 17.1 Current State
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The app uses a **custom ad-hoc language system** with these characteristics:
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- No locale files, no translation dictionaries, no i18n library
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.692Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| **Dictionary Panel** (`dictionaryPanel.ts`) | Quick word lookup on double-click — may conflict with page functionality |
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Language is propagated as a parameter to every AI generation function
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Vietnamese responses are generated via `if (language === 'vietnamese')` branching
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- `meaningVi` fields assume Vietnamese is the only second language worth storing
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### 17.2 Required Changes for Globalization
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- `type Language = 'english' | 'vietnamese' | 'both'` in multiple files
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - `aiExplanationLanguage` — language for AI tutor explanations
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - `nativeLanguage` — user's native language (for translation features)
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - `contentLanguage` — language for exercise content/instructions
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +2. **Remove hard-coded Vietnamese branching:**
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Replace `if (language === 'vietnamese')` with `if (language === userSettings.aiExplanationLanguage)`
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - `appDisplayLanguage` — language for UI chrome/menus/buttons
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Replace hardcoded Vietnamese strings with AI-generated translations or locale files
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +3. **Data model changes:**
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Remove `'vietnamese'` from `AiTutorMode`, `TutorTone`, `AiExplainType`; make language a separate dimension
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Remove `useVietnamese` boolean (duplicates `language` field)
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +4. **AI prompt changes:**
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Make language instruction dynamic: `Respond in {language} only.`
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Remove `meaningVi` from core vocabulary schema; replace with language-agnostic `translations: Record<string, string>`
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Remove hardcoded Vietnamese-specific prompts
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Remove Vietnamese-specific schema fields from AI responses
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +5. **Default settings:**
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T08:57:50.693Z] [INFO] [stderr] +   - Vietnamese available as an option, not the default
